her's model was able to explain several statistical\nproperties of the landscapes - including mean and standard deviation of\nselection and epistasis coefficients -, it was often unable to explain the full\nstructure of fitness landscapes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jul 2015 18:08:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Sep 2015 17:08:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 May 2016 14:44:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-18"}
