tions of this phenomenon are presented. From these discussions a\ngeneric picture of OQSs emerges in which the environmentally-mediated coupling\nbetween different quantum states plays a critical role in governing the system\nbehavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jul 2015 12:29:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Nov 2015 17:46:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-06"}
